headline: CF Industries Holdings, Inc. Declares Quarterly Dividend and Confirms Dates for Fourth Quarter 2025 Results and Conference Call
summary: NORTHBROOK, Ill., January 27, 2026--CF Industries Holdings, Inc. (NYSE: CF) today reported that its board of directors has declared a $0.50 per share dividend on its common stock. The dividend will be payable on February 27, 2026, to stockholders of record as of February 13, 2026.

headline: CF & POET Partner to Advance Low-Carbon Pathway for U.S. Ethanol
summary: CF Industries and POET launch a pilot program to track low-carbon fertilizer to corn and ethanol, aiming to cut carbon intensity across the supply chain
